{"tid":287073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人類嚮往美好既事物 同時又想睇到事實","createTime":"2017-06-17T06:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T13:35:04.000Z","uid":14440,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfe00d8f74d3bdb5e5772c64391e3fe7f1aef99","tid":287073,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:45:31.000Z","msg":"而事實就係 哩個世界無野係美好<br />\n愈了解得多 就只會愈醜惡<br />\n點到即止 先可以保留初心 保留美好既一面<br />\n人生若只如初見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/144312_fa423ef31a01a1e400f03d1cabf2f9b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F144312_fa423ef31a01a1e400f03d1cabf2f9b5.jpg&h=1c84c0d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cf2f2668a4a05931f777591cb6093661e173768","tid":287073,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"},{"pid":"0645141e186fa94dcf241091835c07ea9baaab02","tid":287073,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇唔明</blockquote><br />\n睇一次灰一次"},{"pid":"84a0e04e67224808d0dc70f15c97e8726caacdd1","tid":287073,"uid":73650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7a3b3f9fb26ccdb4b47d0c751dafcfb31757e1","tid":287073,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"我明喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebeef2bc2ab40fa338355689782949960475d66","tid":287073,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebfb80f3d0ddf18f2947dac0127eaac25b37031f","tid":287073,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我深信人性本惡"},{"pid":"07d77bb74fce52453595c6852ed6049d60b5c0f6","tid":287073,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"反而我覺得相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以沈溺係美好一面，要去睇去接觸醜真實個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631517c7f43a0dc40db1a0eb0e55d728744e289a","tid":287073,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而我覺得相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以沈溺係美好一面，要去睇去接觸醜真實個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知道左最醜陋嗰一面 自己去作心態上既調適<br />\n再繼續前行<br />\n但絕對唔係知道完之後 覺得天崩地裂<br />\n人呢 就大家都極醜惡架啦<br />\n但真心難求 而哩樣野 先係可以幫你真正脫離地獄"}]}